The [[crystal halberd]] is a degradeable halberd, which can be purchased from [[Islwyn]] for 750,000 coins, after completion of the hard tier of the [[Western Provinces Diary]]. It lasts for 2,500 attacks before it reverts to a [[crystal weapon seed]], which must be recharged for a fee by [[Ilfeen]], or by using [[crystal shard]]s at a [[singing bowl]].

